SELECT I_ITEM_ID, SUM(TOTAL_SALES) AS TOTAL_SALES
FROM (SELECT *
FROM (SELECT t3.i_item_id AS I_ITEM_ID, SUM(store_sales.ss_ext_sales_price) AS TOTAL_SALES
FROM store_sales
INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM date_dim
WHERE d_year = 1998 AND d_moy = 9) AS t ON store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk = t.d_date_sk
INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM customer_address
WHERE ca_gmt_offset = -5) AS t0 ON store_sales.ss_addr_sk = t0.ca_address_sk
INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM item
WHERE i_item_id IN (SELECT i_item_id AS I_ITEM_ID
FROM item
WHERE i_category = 'Music')) AS t3 ON store_sales.ss_item_sk = t3.i_item_sk
GROUP BY t3.i_item_id
UNION ALL
